title: FDOT District 5 -- Law Enforcement Stations, Florida, 2006
name: FDOT District 5 -- Law Enforcement Stations, Florida, 2006
description: This dataset contains law enforcement departments this includes city, county and state highway patrol stations for the FDOT District 5 area. This GIS layer was produced by Data Transfer Solutions (DTS) under contract with FDOT District 5 in 2006. This is one of many layers that fall into the general category of "sociocultural" GIS data.
